---
title: Middle Eastern Roast Pumpkin & Chicken Bowl with Pearl Couscous & Garlic Dip
description: A roast pumpkin and chicken bowl sounds so nourishing and refreshing, especially when there’s some warm Middle Eastern flavours. The touch of chermoula really brings everything together and adds an extra burst of flavour to the pearl couscous. We’re feeling rejuvenated already!
